 ABUJA - Department of State Services (DSS) has said that it is ready to release detained convener of the 'Revolution Now' movement, Omoyele Sowore. November 13, 2019 In "News" A group of protesters, yesterday, stormed the headquarters of the Department of State Services, DSS, over  continued detention of the convener of the #RevolutionNow protest, Omoyele Sowore, and his deputy, Olawale Bakare. November 13, 2019 In "News" Recall that Sowore was arrested in Lagos on August 3 and subsequently flown to Abuja where he is being detained. November 11, 2019 In "News"